nest_core_interval

nest_core_interval

nest_core_interval(data, type, interval, divide)

Arguments

data

Must include, at minimun, following columns: 1. AccountNumber -- Unique numeric identifier -- 2. Date -- Daily consecutive -- 3. Count -- Must include all real numbers --
type

Must be one of following strings: 1. "years" 2. "months" 3. "weeks" 4. "days"
interval

Must be positive integer excluding zero
divide

Must be one of following strings: 1. "A" 2. "R" 3. "L"

Value

nested tibble

Examples
